did.abstract: This collection of photographs come from several events and groups in the ILR School. We have photographs from the Groat & Alpern Award receptions, Commencement, Alumni Awards, and many photographs of the new ILR building, faculty, Alumni, and Alumni Association.

defitem.label: Contact Information:
defitem.item: Kheel Center for Labor-Management Documentation and Archives Martin P. Catherwood Library 227 Ives Hall Cornell University Ithaca, NY 14853 (607) 255-3183> kheel_center@cornell.edu http://www.ilr.cornell.edu/library/kheel-center

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This collection of photographs come from several events and groups in the ILR School. We have photographs from the Groat & Alpern Award receptions, Commencement, Alumni Awards, and many photographs of the new ILR building, faculty, Alumni, and Alumni Association.
